				<span class="single-line" ng-switch-when="11">You are awesome!</span>
				<span class="single-line" ng-switch-when="12">Log in!</span>
				<span class="single-line" ng-switch-when="13">YA!</span>
				<span ng-switch-when="14">There is now cow level.</span>
				<span ng-switch-when="15">Snape kills Dumbledore.</span>
				<span class="small" ng-switch-when="16">Rubber baby buggy bumpers.</span>
